# py-trans
```py
from py_trans import PyTranslator

tr = PyTranslator()
print(tr.google("Hi", "es"))
```

<p align="center">
  A Fast, hassle-free way to translate text ðŸ“–
<p>

<p align="center">
  <kbd><a href="#features"><b>Features</b></a></kbd>
